description._content: Description: Mounted Forest Guard's house being built in 1926, at Laxia tou Spyrou, Xylotymbo Forest, Elevation 180 feet above sea level. Location: Cyprus Date: 1926 Description: Mounted Forest Guard's house at Laxia tou Spyrou showing growth of trees 8 years old by 1933, Xylotymbo Forest, 180 feet above sea level. Location: Cyprus Date: 1933 Our Catalogue Reference: Part of CO 1069/698 This image is part of the Colonial Office photographic collection held at The National Archives. Feel free to share it within the spirit of the Commons Please use the comments section below the pictures to share any information you have about the people, places or events shown. We have attempted to provide place information for the images automatically but our software may not have found the correct location.
